<view class="page" wx:if="{{!loading && correction}}"><view class="section"><text class="title">处理食材纠错</text><text class="subtitle">核对原始快照与当前食材后再决定是否修改。</text></view><view class="section card"><view class="summary-head"><view><text class="food-name">{{correction.food_name}}</text><text class="muted-text">{{correction.correction_type_text}}</text></view><text class="status status-{{correction.status}}">{{correction.status_text}}</text></view><text class="description">{{correction.description}}</text><text wx:if="{{correction.suggested_value}}" class="suggested">用户建议：{{correction.suggested_value}}</text><text wx:if="{{correction.applied_food_update}}" class="applied-note">该纠错已同步修改过平台食材</text></view><view class="section snapshot"><text class="section-title">提交时数据</text><view class="snapshot-grid"><text>热量 {{correction.food_snapshot.calorie_per_100g}}</text><text>蛋白 {{correction.food_snapshot.protein_per_100g}}g</text><text>碳水 {{correction.food_snapshot.carb_per_100g}}g</text><text>脂肪 {{correction.food_snapshot.fat_per_100g}}g</text></view></view><view class="section card form-card"><view class="field"><text class="label">处理状态 *</text><picker range="{{statuses}}" range-key="label" value="{{statusIndex}}" bindchange="changeStatus"><view class="picker-value">{{statuses[statusIndex].label}}</view></picker></view><view class="field"><text class="label">管理员说明</text><textarea class="textarea" maxlength="500" value="{{adminNote}}" placeholder="填写核对结果或未采纳原因" bindinput="inputNote"></textarea></view><view class="switch-row"><view><text class="label">同步修改食材</text><text class="muted-text">{{correction.applied_food_update ? '该记录已完成同步。' : '仅“已采纳”状态可开启。'}}</text></view><switch checked="{{applyFoodUpdate}}" disabled="{{!food || correction.applied_food_update}}" color="#16a05d" bindchange="toggleApply"/></view></view><view class="section card form-card" wx:if="{{applyFoodUpdate && food}}"><text class="section-title">确认修改后的食材数据</text><view class="field"><text class="label">食材名称 *</text><input class="input" value="{{food.name}}" data-field="name" bindinput="inputFood"/></view><view class="field"><text class="label">食材分类</text><picker range="{{categories}}" range-key="name" value="{{categoryIndex}}" bindchange="changeCategory"><view class="picker-value">{{categories[categoryIndex].name || '未分类'}}</view></picker></view><view class="nutrition-grid"><view class="field"><text class="label">热量</text><input class="input" type="digit" value="{{food.calorie_per_100g}}" data-field="calorie_per_100g" bindinput="inputFood"/></view><view class="field"><text class="label">蛋白质</text><input class="input" type="digit" value="{{food.protein_per_100g}}" data-field="protein_per_100g" bindinput="inputFood"/></view><view class="field"><text class="label">碳水</text><input class="input" type="digit" value="{{food.carb_per_100g}}" data-field="carb_per_100g" bindinput="inputFood"/></view><view class="field"><text class="label">脂肪</text><input class="input" type="digit" value="{{food.fat_per_100g}}" data-field="fat_per_100g" bindinput="inputFood"/></view></view><text class="muted-text">以上营养数据按每 100g 填写。</text></view><view class="save-button" role="button" bindtap="save">{{saving ? '正在保存...' : '保存处理结果'}}</view></view><view class="page" wx:elif="{{loadFailed}}"><view class="card empty"><text class="empty-title">纠错详情加载失败</text><view class="secondary-button retry" role="button" bindtap="loadPage">重新加载</view></view></view><view class="loading-state" wx:else>正在加载纠错详情...</view>
